# Cog writes out the centre of mass or geometry
# of the solute molecules in your trajectory.
# Your solute molecules are replaced by single-
# atom molecules, or these single molecules can
# be added to your trajectory after every solute molecule
#
#
@topo mysys.top
@pbc r
@traj mysys.trj
# Skip every nth frame (default=1)
@nthframe 16
# Do you want to write out the centre of mass (com)
# or the centre of geometry (cog) ?
@cog_com cog
# Do you want to add or replace the com or cog?
# (add or repl)
@add_repl repl
